Vector Capital May Buy Ness for $300 Million, Calcalist Reports

-- B y   J o n a t h a n   F e r z i g e r
-- 
2011-04-04T05:13:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-04/vector-capital-may-buy-ness-for-300-million-calcalist-reports.html
Vector Capital Corp., a San
Francisco-based venture capital firm, is in advanced talks to
buy  Ness Technologies Inc. (NSTC)  for $300 million, Calcalist said
without saying where it got the information. A call made to Ness
before office hours went unanswered.  Click here for web link  To contact the reporter on this story:
